rder, which determines the search priority when algorithms are requested without an explicit provider specification.\n\nThe architecture implements a service discovery pattern where Cipher.getInstance() queries the Security class for available providers, which are loaded from both the java.security configuration file and dynamically registered providers, each offering cryptographic services via their registered Service objects."
